{"title_page": "2005 World Wrestling Championships", "text_new": "{{Infobox FILA wrestling event\n|Name = 2005 World Championships\n|Logo = 2005 FILA Wrestling World Championships logo.png\n|Size = 110\n|Host city ={{flagicon|HUN}} [[Budapest]], [[Hungary]]\n|Optional caption =\n|Events = \n|dates = 26 September \u2013 2 October\n|Stadium = [[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 Papp Budapest Sports Arena]]\n|Freestyle = {{RUS}}\n|Greco-Roman = {{HUN}}\n|Women = {{JPN}}\n|Previous = [[2003 World Wrestling Championships|2003]]\n|Next = [[2006 World Wrestling Championships|2006]]\n}}\n\nThe '''2005 [[World Wrestling Championships]]''' were held at the [[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 Papp Budapest Sports Arena]] in [[Budapest]], [[Hungary]]. The event took place from September 26 to October 2, 2005.\n\n==Medal table==\n{{Medals table\n | caption        = \n | host           = \n | flag_template  = flagcountry\n | event          = \n | team           = \n | gold_RUS = 5 | silver_RUS = 1 | bronze_RUS = 3\n | gold_JPN = 4 | silver_JPN = 1 | bronze_JPN = 1\n | gold_BUL = 2 | silver_BUL = 2 | bronze_BUL = 1\n | gold_CHN = 2 | silver_CHN = 2 | bronze_CHN = 1\n | gold_TUR = 2 | silver_TUR = 0 | bronze_TUR = 2\n | gold_CUB = 1 | silver_CUB = 3 | bronze_CUB = 2\n | gold_GEO = 1 | silver_GEO = 1 | bronze_GEO = 1\n | gold_IRI = 1 | silver_IRI = 1 | bronze_IRI = 1\n | gold_USA = 1 | silver_USA = 0 | bronze_USA = 6\n | gold_BLR = 1 | silver_BLR = 0 | bronze_BLR = 2 | name_BLR = {{flagcountry|BLR|1995}}\n | gold_UZB = 1 | silver_UZB = 0 | bronze_UZB = 0\n | gold_HUN = 0 | silver_HUN = 4 | bronze_HUN = 3\n | gold_KOR = 0 | silver_KOR = 2 | bronze_KOR = 0 | name_KOR = {{flagcountry|KOR|1997}}\n | gold_UKR = 0 | silver_UKR = 1 | bronze_UKR = 3\n | gold_CAN = 0 | silver_CAN = 1 | bronze_CAN = 2\n | gold_DEN = 0 | silver_DEN = 1 | bronze_DEN = 0\n | gold_FRA = 0 | silver_FRA = 1 | bronze_FRA = 0\n | gold_GER = 0 | silver_GER = 0 | bronze_GER = 2\n | gold_KAZ = 0 | silver_KAZ = 0 | bronze_KAZ = 2\n | gold_MGL = 0 | silve